## Run auth.http → Login first to populate {{token}}

### Get spellbook (learned spells + mana)
GET {{host}}/spells
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
## ─── Auto-learnable spells (level 1-3) ───
###

### Learn Mana Surge (mage, spell level 2, char level 3 required)
POST {{host}}/spells/learn
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "spellId": "mana-surge"
}

### Learn Arcane Intellect (mage, spell level 2, char level 3 required)
POST {{host}}/spells/learn
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "spellId": "arcane-intellect"
}

