###
## ─── Scroll-only spells (level 4-5) — learn endpoint should REJECT these ───
###

### Try to learn Counterspell via /learn — should fail (spell level 4, needs scroll)
POST {{host}}/spells/learn
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "spellId": "counterspell"
}

### Try to learn Blizzard via /learn — should fail (spell level 5, needs scroll)
POST {{host}}/spells/learn
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "spellId": "blizzard"
}

### Try to learn Holy Nova via /learn — should fail (spell level 4, needs scroll)
POST {{host}}/spells/learn
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "spellId": "holy-nova"
}

###
## ─── Casting spells ───
###

### Cast Heal (cleric starting spell — heals 25 HP)
POST {{host}}/spells/cast
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "spellId": "heal"
}

### Cast Nature's Blessing (ranger starting spell — heals 15 HP)
POST {{host}}/spells/cast
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "spellId": "natures-blessing"
}

### Cast Battle Cry (warrior starting spell — buff strength +2)
POST {{host}}/spells/cast
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "spellId": "battle-cry"
}

### Cast Bless (cleric starting spell — buff wisdom +2)
POST {{host}}/spells/cast
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "spellId": "bless"
}

### Cast Mana Surge (mage — restore 30 mana, 0 cost, requires learning first)
POST {{host}}/spells/cast
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "spellId": "mana-surge"
}

### Cast Teleport (mage — teleport to town, requires learning first)
POST {{host}}/spells/cast
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "spellId": "teleport"
}

### Cast Arcane Intellect (mage — buff intelligence +2, requires learning first)
POST {{host}}/spells/cast
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "spellId": "arcane-intellect"
