###
## ─── Error cases ───
###

### Cast a combat spell — should fail outside of battle
POST {{host}}/spells/cast
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "spellId": "magic-missile"
}

### Try to learn a spell for the wrong class
POST {{host}}/spells/learn
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "spellId": "fireball"
}

### Try to cast a spell you haven't learned
POST {{host}}/spells/cast
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "spellId": "blizzard"
}
